Bhai tere jaise genuine friends boht kam hi mile hain IITK me, hamesha dependable. 
First year me tere saath saare course kare, CC me saath me nightouts, wing me almost roz alag level bakchodi to yaad rahegi hi. Nami me pizza nights. Pingala jo fek ke maara tha bomb ki tareh uss din kya dhamaka kiya tha bhai god level. Vo iskon temple ki trip tere saath yaad aati hai.

Sabse mehenti logo me se .

Par kabhi milenge zaroor !!!!
author: Geetam

text:
Aur bhai Train gawd kaafi lamba hone wala hai ye bsdk.
Abhi bhi bura lagta hai yaar hum first year start se dost nahi the, tere jaisa harami/genuine/mastikhor launda 100% pure gold hai IITK me.
ICPC me jo fraud hua tha aur paisa barbaad hua tha vo to kabhi nahi bhulunga bhai ğŸ¤£, bc ukhada kuch nahi but bulla boht kata.
Vo kalyanpur mithai quest yaad aati hai jab har jageh ghum rahe the DIwali pe patakhe aur mithai dhundhne.
Yaar Covid ke baad last ke 2 mahine maximum maze tere saath hi hue hain, na jane kitni baar to campus ghumaya tune nayi nayi jageh jo pata bhi nahi thi dikhayi aur kisse sunaye.
Pehli baar suna tha bc train me hi chaap ke aaya launda, awsar ko apada bana diya ğŸ”¥ğŸ”¥ğŸ”¥.
Puri raat UNO, bluff aur "kuch logo" ke maze lene me nikal jati thi.
Par jitne maze karaye tune bsdk utni zyada gaand bhi mari hai teri vajeh se saale. kamar tudwa di thi uss din football ground me jiska dard abhi tak nahi gaya. 
Aur bsdk finger fracture bhi ho gaya tha teri hi throw catch karne me saale jahan tere saath hota hun vahan kuch na kuch injury ho hi jati hai merko.
Covid ke time hospital trip to yaad hogi hi, tu bc chote se fracture ke liye meri surgery karane ko tayaar ho gaya tha(" arre 90% refund milra hai 4000 Rs hi lagenge bas, karale bhai surgery, mai hota to kara leta").ğŸ˜¡ğŸ˜¡
Tera vo road accident sunke bc dimaag kharab ho gaya tha yaar, end me jo hua badhiya bach gaya sahi se.
Vo daru nasha night mai kabhi nahi bhul sakta, tu bc bada shareef banra tha (bas bhais ka dudh pita hun mai), uske baad pata nahi kya kya piya tune bhi.
Bhai last ke week dur ho gaye the uska dukh to hai hi, par Chandigarh/Shimla ka plan hamesha on hai.
Milte hain bhai jald hi.
author: Geetam

text:
Aur bhai Salad gawd. Barbeque me khana to zyada variety ka mila nahi kisiko but tu bada khush tha yaar anek tareh ke salad khakar ğŸ˜‚. Vo iskon temple trip me kitne maze kare the. Bithoor trip to tere saath puri zindagi yaad rahegi 15km ke raaste kamse kam 10 baar ruke the teri cycle ki chain theek karne ko ğŸ˜‚. Wing me full on bakchodi, exam time me saath me padhayi, aur inn sab me Shailabh ki constant saath me gaand maarna, kya unique memories bani hai yaar tere saath. EE380 ki lab me jitne maze kare the bas likhte hue hi hasi aa rahi hai bc, jab tune control wale TA ke pas me hi bol diya tha "jhooth bol dete hain isko"ğŸ˜‚ . Itne saare courses kare tere saath gin na bhi mushkil. Aur Placement ki jo gaand maarli yaar tune, aisa gadar chaapa ki sabhi ka ctc tere base se kam hai bc.
Yaad aayegi yaar teri, abhi bhi boht aati hai. Bas umeed hai mulakaat hoti rahe hamesha !!!
author: Geetam

text:
Bhai bas kya kehne yaar tere KG.
First year me almost bina baat kare bhi closest friend bangaya, campus me sabse dependable bando mein se. Officially nahi par roommate hi the pure time. Agra me Delhi ki vajeh se airport na hone ki teri tatti theory sunke pehli baar pata laga tha yaar iss launde me kuch baat hai.
Vo railway wale bhaiya se jo Agra to Kanpur train me chai nashta mangwata tha, yaad rahega bhai. Hall ka canteen gawd, kabhi bhi kehlo canteen jane ko tayaar chahe sote hue ko bhi maar ke utha do. 1 saal puri raat PUBG khelke sem thukwaye the par jo yaadein bani. Bakchodi ka jo alag level hota tha roz has haske dard ho jata tha yaar.
Tere saath Manali trip kabhi nahi bhul sakta bhai. Free stay dilaya tha camp me, jo mast RR kara tha tune rappelling karte waqt maza hi aa gaya tha. 
Online sem me jo Dassa laake wing tabah kiya tha kya kehne bc. 
Abhi jab corona ke baad 2 mahine aake jo aakhri nightouts aur UNO,bluff nights, vo ek nashili nightout highlight thi. 
Sochne me bhi bura lagta hai bhai ki ab itna mil nahi payenge.

Boht maze liye hain tune saale vo Vox populi wala to yaad hi hoga maar hi li thi, messgage bhi delete kardiye the bsdk pata bhi nahi laga tha kya chod failaya hai next din tak.

Vo galaxy me maze yaad aate hain, aur TA nights to itni yaadgaar rahi bc. Monday vaale sacrifice deke blueprint dete aur hum Thursday wale chill maarke group me masti karte hue figures chaap ke full late.

text:
Aur bhai Goldman.
1st year me wing me na hone pe bhi wingie hi tha tu!! puri degree hi saath hui hai apni, maximum courses me teri meherbani aur tere chaapne se grade mila hai, tere saath hi wing me masti kari, roz canteen me chai pi.
Tu hi ek banda mila hai jo sabki tareh chill maarta hai, padhta zyada nahi par bc phir bhi magguon se better grade le aata hai.
Tere saath jo projects me frauds maare hain vo to kabhi bhul hi nahi sakta mai. Jab bhi sochta hun bc hasi aa jati hai kitne hi profs ka kaatkar resume bhara hai. Khaaskar vo particular Deep learning wala project to yaad hi hoga jisse kuch zyada hi help ho gayi meri !!!ğŸ¤£ğŸ¤£ğŸ¤£
 Vo ek pura PUBG wala saal jab puri raat hi PUBG me nikal jaati thi grades ki mar gayi thi par tere nahi yaar tu chaap hi deta hai. Summer me dono ne jamkar Critical Ops khela coding kuch nahi kari par tu bc pehle din hi Goldman ban gaya, tab pata laga yaar Groot to kisi tareh bina kuch tayari kare bhi chaap hi lega, apna dekho bc !!!!
Iskon temple aur bithoor trip me boht maza aaya tha yaar itni dur tak pehli baar cycling kari thi humne.
Barbeque aur Pizza hut me bhi khoob maze kar rakhe hain.
Abhi covid ke baad to mil nahi paye but ab dono ki location Bangalore hi hai, Jald hi milte hain !!!.
